      <title>乌克兰无人机袭击导致俄罗斯大型炼油厂起火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ukrainian-drone-attack-sets-major-russian-oil-refinery-on-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰无人机袭击了位于莫斯科东南部梁赞的国有俄罗斯石油公司旗下的一家大型炼油厂，当时该炼油厂的原油加工刚刚从之前的袭击中恢复过来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ukrainian-drone-attack-sets-major-russian-oil-refinery-on-fire</guid>
