      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/georgia-crisis-erupts-after-violent-clashes-over-russian-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟表示，“强烈”谴责格鲁吉亚防暴警察在因有争议的“外国代理人”法而发生一夜暴力冲突后对抗议者采取的镇压行动。]]></description>
